        "description": {
            "value": "<p>All creatures in the area when you cast the spell are limned in colorful, heatless fire of a color of your choice for the duration. Visible creatures can't be @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} while affected by faerie fire. If the creatures are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.zJxUflt9np0q4yML]{Invisible}, they are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} while affected by faerie fire, rather than being @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.VRSef5y1LmL2Hkjf]{Undetected}.</p>",
